# ============================================
# MAINNET Environment Configuration
# ============================================
# This configuration is for PRODUCTION deployment on Oasys Mainnet
#
# Network: Oasys Hub Layer (Mainnet)
# Chain ID: 248
# RPC URL: https://rpc.mainnet.oasys.games
#
# IMPORTANT: Use Fireblocks for mainnet deployments!
